anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 24px; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">每个剧本，就像一部独立的三国历史剧，不仅细节可考，还设置了独特的任务与目标。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dpu8C _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 24px; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">你会发现&mdash;&mdash;某一次，你是曹操，要在十回合统一北方；下一次，你可能是刘备，只能靠结盟与人心去逆转战局。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dpu8C _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 24px; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">每一局的起点、任务都不同，每一局都是全新的故事。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"_3hMwG _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; display: flex; margin-top: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;</div>', '002', '是');
INSERT INTO `biji` VALUES (4, '112621273127', '和四个妹子流落荒岛游戏初体验——《孤岛笔记》', '/upload/a06f77705c55aed90182e06d6746ee39.png', '7,4,3', 2, '/upload/23f8df02bb6a6fb3c1d8d1171595f1a0.mp4', 1, 0, '<div class=\"dpu8C _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 21px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.7;\">漂亮妹妹陪你在孤岛生存</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dpu8C _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 24px; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">不懂就问，假如现实里的你因为种种原因流落到了一个全是变异生物的荒岛上。没有金手指不能开挂，但好处是有一堆漂亮妹妹在你身边天天围着你，而且不愁吃不愁喝不会生病。你还想回去吗？</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dpu8C _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 24px; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">反正我是不想，已在《孤岛笔记》安家，没事勿Q</p>\n<div class=\"dpu8C _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 28px; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 21px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.7;\">男女搭配，干活不累</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dpu8C _2kCxD  \" style=\"overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space: normal; word-break: normal; text-wrap-style: unset !important; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 24px; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; overflow-wrap: anywhere; white-space-collapse: collapse; word-break: normal; text-wrap: unset !important; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">游戏主玩法是流落荒岛模拟生存，有一切生存游戏需要面临的困境：饥饿、口渴、生命值与体力值等；还有经典的模拟生存玩法，从0到1建设属于自己的孤岛。不过与硬核生存游戏不同的是，这里有漂亮妹子和你一起流落荒岛，男女搭配，干活不累。</p>\n</div>\n</div>', '001', '是');

